            	<li>Methodology is inadequate or insufficient to support conclusions</li>
            	<li>Controls are absent or inadequate</li>
            	<li>Statistical evaluation is absent or inadequate</li>
            	<li>Summary of essential results is absent or inadequate</li>
            	<li>Data are not included or offer inadequate/insufficient support for conclusions
Submission reports clinical trial data from unplanned analysis or incomplete or ongoing studies</li>
